Class SegmentImpl

java.lang.Object
  se.dat255.bulletinferno.model.map.SegmentImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
com.badlogic.gdx.utils.Disposable, Segment
public class SegmentImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements Segment

An implementation of the Segment interface. A Segment is one more many "map slices" that fit together both by size and in-game look. Use an appropriate SegmentDefinition to get help creating the Segment.

See Also:
